<P>Quem dicunt homines esse fil. hominis&mdash;</P>
<LG>
<L N="25">"Omang &thorn;e folk here whor &yogh;e wun<NOTE PLACE="foot">Whilk of all here whare &yogh;e won</NOTE></L>
