<L>And sum said it was John Baptist<NOTE PLACE="foot">And sum men als toke John B.</NOTE></L>
<L>Man sun, in stede of Jhesu Crist,<NOTE PLACE="foot">In &thorn;e stede of Jhesu Crist.</NOTE></L>
<L N="55">And sum, o&thorn;er prophettes of &thorn;e law &mdash;<NOTE PLACE="foot">prophetes.</NOTE></L>
