<L>On &thorn;is maner he sayd &thorn;am till:<NOTE PLACE="foot">wise.</NOTE></L>
<L>"What say &yogh;e of me &yogh;ow al omang<MILESTONE N="153" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="foot">al fehlt.</NOTE></L>
