<L>And &thorn;ou wil for &thorn;is be wrathe,<NOTE PLACE="foot">And sir if &thorn;ou for &thorn;is.</NOTE></L>
<L>&THORN;an wil I warn &thorn;e of &thorn;i skathe;</L>
<L N="95">Al &thorn;e force of &thorn;i fendes grym<NOTE PLACE="foot">&THORN;at all &thorn;i craft of fendes grim.</NOTE></L>
<L>May no-thing help ogayns him.<NOTE PLACE="foot">help &thorn;e vnto him.</NOTE></L>
