<L>Folk to gode bringe,<NOTE PLACE="foot">god bring.</NOTE></L>
<L>&THORN;oru &thorn;is ilke &thorn;inge<NOTE PLACE="foot">&THORN;urch. ich &thorn;ing.</NOTE></L>
