<L>&THORN;at &yogh;e suggen &thorn;ries<NOTE PLACE="foot">sigge.</NOTE></L>
<L N="250">Wi&thorn; wel gode wille</L>
<L>Bo&thorn;e loude and stille<NOTE PLACE="foot">bo&thorn;.</NOTE></L>
<L>&THORN;ese aue maries.<NOTE PLACE="foot">&thorn;is. A. hat darauf noch folg. Schlussstrophe: And god, our alder dri&yogh;t, So &yogh;iue ous streng&thorn;e and mi&yogh;t, So wele for to done, &THORN;at at our ending He mot ous alle bring To blis swi&thorn;e sone. Amen.</NOTE>
</L>
</LG>

