<L>All fulfylled wyth goddus manhode;<NOTE PLACE="foot2">AB And st. all. A fullfyld, B. full. AB of. A goddys, B godys.</NOTE></L>
<L>And ner goddus manhode were,<NOTE PLACE="foot2">A And &yogh;it goddys manhod nere, B And if godys manhode were.</NOTE></L>
