<L>For &thorn;orow hys passyon &amp; hys manhede<NOTE PLACE="foot2">For fehlt in AB. B manhed.</NOTE><NOTE PLACE="foot2">B heuens. AB blys; oure.</NOTE></L>
<L N="80">Heuen blysse shall be her mede.<NOTE PLACE="foot1">Ms. hys st. her?</NOTE>
<PB REF="00000651.tif" N="513"></L>
<L>The sixte heuen holy chyrche ys,<NOTE PLACE="foot2">A sext, B sexte. B chyrch.</NOTE></L>
