<L N="90">That Jhesus hath, our sauyour."<NOTE PLACE="foot2">AB hath Jhesus (B Jhesu). AB oure.</NOTE></L>
<L>The emperour sayde anon ry&yogh;t:<NOTE PLACE="foot2">B seyd anone.</NOTE></L>
<L>"How mony orderus ar &thorn;er of angelus bry&yogh;t?"<NOTE PLACE="foot2">AB many. A ordyrs, B orders. A ben, B be. &thorn;er fehlt in AB.</NOTE></L>
